  "description": "<i>Left Brain, Right Brain</i> is a mind exercise-type game.  Its mini-games are designed to stimulate both the right and left hemispheres of the brain and make the user ambidextrous.<br><br>It has 15 mini-games that you can play, including Connect the Dots, Pop the Balloons, Feel the Music, Hit the Monsters, Touch the Green Square, Save the World, Open the Safe, Trace the Shape, Navigate the Maze and more and has five different difficulty settings.<br><br>It also has four single player game modes (Hand Exercises, Balance Check, Left Hand vs. Right Hand and Ambidexterity Check) and keeps track of your progress and helps you out to improve in certain areas.<br><br>You can also go head to head against a friend using the DS download play.",
